                                        <div class="ctpl-c-faq_accordion-header-content">
                                            What are the responsibilities of the employer when a worker makes a claim?
                                        </div>
                                        <div aria-hidden="true" class="ctpl-c-faq_accordion-header-button">
                                            <i></i>
                                        </div>
                                    </button>
                                        <div class="ctpl-c-faq_accordion-content" id="6d65944a-5241-4f48-8ffa-1c02bf248c5e" role="region" aria-labelledby="accordion-id-6d65944a-5241-4f48-8ffa-1c02bf248c5e" tabindex="0">
                                            <ul>
    <li>Complete and submit the employment verification form</li>
    <li>Validate absences and sources of money as needed</li>
    <li>Notify worker about its paid time off (PTO) policies (including short-term disability policies)</li>
    <li>Refrain from discriminating or retaliating against worker for filing a CT Paid Leave claim</li>
</ul>
